snippet.title: Diana Pretend Play with Baby doll and toys!
snippet.description:
Diana pretend play with toys for kids. Little girl wakes up with her  Baby Alive doll, and then playing with her in the hide and seek. Diana had a super fun day with Baby doll. They even washed dishes together and learned. And in the evening Diana put the doll to sleep. Good video for kids with Baby Alive and girls toys.
